The valid special segment and gate descriptor types for LSL are given
in the following table:

Type   Name                      Valid/Invalid

  0    Invalid                   Invalid
  1    Available 80286 TSS       Valid
  2    LDT                       Valid
  3    Busy 80286 TSS            Valid
